title: Joe Buscaino
added: Buscaino is a first-generation Italian-American, whose parents [[emigrated]] from [[Italy]] over 40 years ago.{{source?|date=January 2021}} Buscaino graduated [[cum laude]], with a [[Bachelor of Arts|B.A.]] in [[Communication studies|communications]] from [[California State University, Dominguez Hills]], in 1996.{{source?|date=January 2021}}
